snippet.title: Just Another Night Shift | Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Just Another Night Shift is a casual competitive 1vs1 strategy game. Join us for hours of fun gameplay with your friends! 

Wishlisht the game on Steam! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2331130/Just_Another_Night_Shift/



Game is currently in alpha state, expect gameplay, graphics and sounds to be changed over time. Release date Q1 2024.
“Additional sound effects from https://www.zapsplat.com“
